result.name: Siu Choi Wong

reviews.text: Food is good but pricy. Come here if you want a very happening place (aka  noisy).
Traditional HK street food
Goat pot is superb. Salad pork chop very good, deep fried intestines very crunchy,.

Lots of places to sit, helpful manager will gladly assist. Check out the fish and seafood still alive😚😎 choose what you want and they will cook to order. Recommend so many dishes, they are big so best to share most of them. Little salty and maybe msg but I like it. Goes great with a cold beer or two.
good stop for dinner with wide selection of stir fried chinese food

result.name: New Yung Kee

reviews.text: A very nice local restaurant located in Shamshuipo area suitable for big group for enjoyable dinner.
best crispy pork belly i ever taste
Great food! Very busy during dinner times and usually have long queue outside. Surprisingly the dishes came pretty quick, but don't expect to receive much service.
Food portion is big, roast pork is one of the signature dish.
Char siu and seafood highly recommended . With fresh beer . Great place to go with friend!!

result.adr_address: 香港元洲福華街118號
result.name: 容記小菜王

reviews.text: 還以為是吃小菜的地方，原來下午茶也有奶茶咖啡飲。
食物唔夠熱辣辣， 最出名的墨魚嘴也不新鮮， 質素有點失望了
午市套餐價錢實惠 地點方便
小菜味道不錯，每碟份量大份，好有港式大排檔風味，價格適中

男性朋友帶路，去深水埗福華街118號，新容記小菜王。原來有三間鋪一齊。
晚飯三個人先後叫了五碟餸，包括：燒腩仔(例牌128元)、南乳粗齋煲 ($68)、燒汁薯仔牛柳粒($128)、鐵板醬燒釀茄子($98)、豉椒炒蟶子($48一隻，共$144)，埋單仲要加一
